data.description: This property offers breathtaking views of the Bennett mountains, farm ground, and even includes its own mountain, making it a remarkable find for nature lovers, horse lovers and those seeking tranquility. The property just shy of 5 acres also boasts beautiful flowerbeds, perfect for those with a green thumb. The kitchen has recently been updated in 2022, bringing a modern touch to the home. Master bedroom with a half bath, a family room, and a great room, providing ample space for relaxation and entertainment. Possible 3rd bedroom. Additionally, there is a shop available for storing your toys, and enough room around the shop for an RV. You will also find hunting, fishing, boating and so much more. Truly a diamond in the ruff! Second owner of the property. Consumable VA loan, possible.
